summary: Borrowed from Positive_Who on Twitter, I’m going to post a gif each day for each category.  If you’re on Twitter, check them...
body:
Say Something Nice Challenge Day 4

Borrowed from Positive_Who on Twitter, I’m going to post a gif each day for each category. If you’re on Twitter, check them out. I love this account, because it’s great. It’s one of the few Twitter spaces where you can just like DW. I definitely enjoy their positivity towards all Doctors and eras.

Day 4: Big Finish Audios

I’m just starting to get into these and I’m really loving them. It’s fun to have something to listen to in the car on the way to work.

Tagging @gingergallifreyan and anyone else who would like to join in!
